<hr><br>

<b><span style="display: inline-block ; height: 30px ; width: 40px ; background: transparent url(&quot;https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/pokemonicons-sheet.png?v16&quot;) no-repeat scroll -360px -2580px"></span>How often does the gallery get updated?</b>
<br><br>The gallery gets updated when its owner:
<li>reviews user submissions.
<li>spots a new trainer card or signups avatar displayed in the room.
<br><br>However, the same trainer card or signups avatar will not get updated twice within a short period of time.

<br><br><b><span style="display: inline-block ; height: 30px ; width: 40px ; background: transparent url(&quot;https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/pokemonicons-sheet.png?v16&quot;) no-repeat scroll -360px -2580px"></span>Any plans to exhibit scripted box, host box, and vote box?</b>
<br><br>There was a plan to exhibit host box, however there were some difficulties in displaying buttons accurately, and thus the idea was dropped. 
<br><br>There are no plans to exhibit scripted box or vote box.

